im-not-ai (Humanize KR)
-----------------------
- Source: https://github.com/epoko77-ai/im-not-ai
- License: MIT

Notepad AI's always-on Korean "AI-tell removal" style layer re-expresses the
AI-tell taxonomy and rewriting playbook concepts from the im-not-ai project as
static TypeScript prompt/rule data (see src/renderer/humanize-taxonomy.ts and
src/renderer/humanize-engine.ts). No source code from im-not-ai is copied
verbatim; the categories and corrective directives are an independent
re-expression of the project's documented taxonomy, used under the MIT license
with attribution.

The English-language humanization taxonomy is an original, minimal, and
explicitly experimental addition by Notepad AI (im-not-ai is Korean-only).
